## .lgo for T1.2 twoN scalar mode (shared=N convention)

### Parameters
time fixed T_z=0
time fixed T_x=0
time fixed T_y=0
time free T_xyz=2
time free T_xy=0.5
twoN fixed shared=1000


### Segments
segment xyz t=T_xyz twoN=shared
segment xy t=T_xy twoN=shared
segment z t=T_z twoN=shared samples=1
segment x t=T_x twoN=shared samples=1
segment y t=T_y twoN=shared samples=1

### Relationships
derive xy from xyz
derive z from xyz
derive x from xy
derive y from xy
